text: The 1896 Washington Agricultural football team was an American football team that represented Washington Agricultural College during the 1896 college football season. The team competed as an independent under head coach David A. Brodie and compiled a record of 2–0–1. ==Schedule== ==References== Washington Agricultural Category:Washington State Cougars football seasons Category:College football undefeated seasons Category:1896 in Washington (state)
